modName: Melinda and Belinda lvl 1 cute young female Bretons save
summary: First I created Melinda (dark hair), some people was interessted in this save game so I made Belinda (blond hair). She is really like a sister for Melinda, quite simmilar only whit subtle changes in apperance.
descriptionHtml:
First I created Melinda (dark hair), some people was interessted in this save game so I made Belinda (blond hair). She is really like a sister for Melinda, quite simmilar only whit subtle changes in apperance. 
They are in a Forge in Riverwood. 

Mods I used

If you want your character to look like the ones on the screenshots, you will need to download and install these mods:

-Better Females by BellaGail, I used and recommended \"No makeup just improved textures\" version
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812

-ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168

-Improved Eyes Skyrim by missjennabee
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9249

Optional: 
-Younger Bretons by Psyke23, Female version, entirely independent and optional
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2637#

Body (optional) :

-DIMONIZED UNP female body by dimon99
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709

-CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible by navetsea
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6554


Remember! The Mods I used for these saved games are not from me. The credits goes to BellaGail, Apachii, dimon99, missjennabee and navetsea. If you like their Mods please remember to endorse them for their great effort!!!

If you like my saved games please endorse them. Thank you very much and enjoy!
